{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 44,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الدُّخَانِ",
    "englishName": "Ad-Dukhaan",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Smoke",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 59,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4415,
        "text": "哈，米目[阿拉伯语二个字母的音译，唯安拉最知道其意]。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4416,
        "text": "以这部明白[阐明万事万物]的经典[《古兰经》]发誓！",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4417,
        "text": "我的确在一个吉庆之夜[斋月的盖德尔夜，见第97章]降示它[《古兰经》]，我一直在警告[人类，凡不信仰安拉独一者必遭严惩]。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4418,
        "text": "在那个夜里，一切注定的事都已判定[如生死灾难等]。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4419,
        "text": "那是由我颁布的一项命令，我确是常派遣使者的；",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4420,
        "text": "那是从你的主降示的一项恩惠。他确是全闻的，全知的。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4421,
        "text": "[那是从]天地万物的主[安拉]降示的，假如你们笃信。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4422,
        "text": "除他外，再没有应受崇拜的主。他能使死者生，能使生者死。[他是]你们的主，也是你们祖先的主。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4423,
        "text": "其实，他们是在怀疑中取乐的。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4424,
        "text": "你当等待天空出现明显烟雾[注]的那日，",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4425,
        "text": "那烟雾将笼罩人类，这是一种痛苦的刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4426,
        "text": "[被烟雾笼罩者将说]：“我们的主啊！求你为我们解除刑罚吧！我们真的信仰了。”",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4427,
        "text": "[刑罚已降临他们，此时]他们怎能获得劝告[的益处]呢？有位明白宣教的使者[穆圣]确已来临他们，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4428,
        "text": "而他们却背离他[穆圣]。他们说：“[他是]一位受过传授的疯子。”",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4429,
        "text": "我将暂时解除刑罚，而你们也将原形毕露[恢复叛逆]。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4430,
        "text": "当我进行大突袭的那日，我必将严惩[他们]。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4431,
        "text": "我确已在他们之前考验过法老的人民，那时有位尊贵的使者[穆萨]已来临他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4432,
        "text": "[穆萨说]：“你们把安拉的仆人们[以色列的后裔]交给我吧！我对你们确是一位忠实的使者。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4433,
        "text": "你们不要对安拉高傲，我的确给你们带来了明证。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4434,
        "text": "我求我的主，也是你们的主保护，免遭你们石击我[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4435,
        "text": "假如你们不相信我，你们可离开我。”",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4436,
        "text": "[但他们挑衅他]，于是他[穆萨]祈求他的主[说]：“这些人确是犯罪的民众。”",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4437,
        "text": "[安拉说]：“你带着我的仆人们在夜间出走吧！因为你们必将被[法老的军队]追赶。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4438,
        "text": "你让海水平静[分开]吧！他们肯定是要被淹死的军队。”",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4439,
        "text": "他们[法老的人民]留下了多少果园、泉源、",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4440,
        "text": "田地和豪宅，",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4441,
        "text": "以及他们享受过的幸福生活！",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4442,
        "text": "其结果是：我使其他民众继承了他们[注][如安拉使以色列的后裔继承了埃及的王权]。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4443,
        "text": "天地没有为他们哭泣，他们也不被缓刑。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4444,
        "text": "—",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4445,
        "text": "我确已拯救以色列的后裔脱离法老凌辱的刑罚。他确是傲慢过分的。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4446,
        "text": "[穆萨时代]我确已凭真知选择他们[以色列的后裔]优于世人。",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4447,
        "text": "我曾赐予他们许多迹象，其中有一次明显的考验。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4448,
        "text": "这些人[古莱什人]必将说：",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4449,
        "text": "“我们只有第一次的死亡，我们绝不会被复活。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4450,
        "text": "假如你们是诚实者，[现在]你们就把我们[已故]的祖先召回来[复活]吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4451,
        "text": "是他们更好呢？还是土巴的族人和他们的前人更好？我毁灭了他们，因为他们确是犯罪者。",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4452,
        "text": "我创造天地万物并非儿戏。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4453,
        "text": "我只依真理[检验谁是顺从安拉者，谁是违抗安拉者；报酬顺从者，惩罚违抗者]创造天地，但他们大多数人并不知道。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4454,
        "text": "判决日确是为他们全体规定的时间。",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4455,
        "text": "在那日，亲友对亲友毫无益处，他们也得不到任何援助，",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4456,
        "text": "唯安拉慈悯者例外[注]。他[安拉]确是全能的，特慈的。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4457,
        "text": "[火狱里]赞古木树的果子，",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4458,
        "text": "确是罪人的食物，",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4459,
        "text": "像铜水一样在[他们的]腹中沸腾，",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4460,
        "text": "像沸水一样沸腾。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4461,
        "text": "[有话声说]：“你们抓住他，把他拖入火狱的中央，",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4462,
        "text": "然后，你们把沸水的刑罚浇在他的头上。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4463,
        "text": "你尝试[这种刑罚]吧！你[在尘世时]是多么妄自尊大、多么富贵！",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4464,
        "text": "这就是你们[在尘世时]所怀疑的[刑罚]。”",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4465,
        "text": "敬畏者必住在安全的地方[乐园]：",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4466,
        "text": "乐园和泉水旁，",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4467,
        "text": "他们穿的是锦绣丝绸，迎面而坐。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4468,
        "text": "其结果是：我使白净美目贤淑的美女做他们的妻子。",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4469,
        "text": "他们在乐园里将安全地索取各种水果。",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4470,
        "text": "除[尘世]第一次的死亡外，他们在乐园里将不再尝试死亡。他[安拉]将保护他们免受火狱的刑罚[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4471,
        "text": "这是从你的主降示的恩惠，这确是伟大的成功。",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4472,
        "text": "我的确以你的语言使这部《古兰经》成为易懂的，以便他们接受劝告。",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4473,
        "text": "你[穆圣]当等待，他们的确也在等待。",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
      "identifier": "zh.mazhonggang",
